OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBreezy, with
OL,6,Frain spreading northeastwards across
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland this
OL,8,Fevening, then some clearer spells
OL,9,Fovernight. Mostly clear for England
OL,10,Fand Wales, though a little patchy fog
OL,11,Fand drizzle is likely in the west. A
OL,12,Fmild night for all.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FPatchy rain and fog in the
OL,15,Fnorthwest, and some western areas at
OL,16,Ffirst. Otherwise dry with a good deal
OL,17,Fof very warm or hot sunshine
OL,18,Fdeveloping. Breezy in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
